+# Research Report: Workflow Execution from UI
+
+**Generated**: 2026-03-13T22:23:00Z
+**Research Query**: "test-pipeline command runs a real pipeline ظ¤ rig into UI for run/stop/restart with live updates via events+state system"
+**Mode**: Pre-Plan
