+**What We're Building**: Contract-level extensions to `drive()`, `OrchestrationService`, `ExecutionStatus`, and `ONBAS` that enable the web execution features in later phases. No web code touched ظ¤ purely the `packages/positional-graph` orchestration engine.
+
+**Goals**:
+- ظ£à `drive()` accepts an `AbortSignal` and returns `'stopped'` when aborted
