+Actually ظ¤ since we need cross-workspace visibility: **user-level** `~/.chainglass/execution-registry.json`. One file, all workspaces, all worktrees.
+
+### Persistence Timing
+
+| Event | Persist? | Why |
+|-------|----------|-----|
+| start() called | Yes | So restart recovery knows to resume |
+| Status changes | Yes | Crash at any point ظْ recovery knows current state |
+| Iteration progress | Debounced (every 10 iterations or 30s) | Avoid write storm |
+| stop() / completion | Yes | Final state |
+| restart() | Yes (delete + add) | Clean slate |
